snippet.textDisplay:
It was mothers Day in North America today so I had my own depictions of the video. When you are tired, hopeless, desperate and darkness everywhere. Your mother is the light to give you strength and hope and even she doesn't know it but it's the divine power granted to her from the heavens. Beautiful song with such beautiful videography. Too short though, these type of masterpieces can go forever and you still won't get enough of it.
On a funnier note, though that Jaffar is giving him hope but in such a sad way that you would get confused.
Hannan using Jaffer's tone in the end carries an important message, look around you and see if someone needs your help, it can be kind words or a hug which can give them something to think about and find a ray of light within. We all can contribute to help someone dealing with loneliness, despair and tough times!!!
